  "description": "A trefoil knot with near-infinite decay — the cross-coupling between all six delay lines ensures the sound never truly resolves, only transforms. Each traversal of the knot filters differently; by the 100th traversal what entered as a piano has become something ancient. This sound began before you played it.",
